;;         | Case              |  found   | index |  order   |     Error      |
;;         +-------------------+----------+-------+----------+----------------+
;;         | x < a[min]        |   FALSE  |  min  |  less    |      0         |
;;         | a[i] < x < a[i+1] |   FALSE  |   i   |  greater |      0         |
;;         | x = a[i]          |   TRUE   |   i   |  equal   |      0         |
;;         | a[max] < x        |   FALSE  |  max  |  greater |      0         |
;;         +-------------------+----------+-------+----------+----------------+
